glpong (1.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release 1.4
  * Updated to modern Debian packaging standards
  * Migrated from SDL1.2 to SDL2
  * Updated to modern OpenGL and OpenAL
  * Fixed memory leaks and various bugs
  * Updated build system to modern autotools and CMake
  * Enhanced fullscreen support with native resolution
  * debian/control: Updated build dependencies for SDL2, modern standards
  * debian/rules: Simplified using modern debhelper
  * debian/compat: Removed in favor of debhelper-compat in control

 -- Erik Greenwald <erik@elfga.com>  Sun, 15 Sep 2025 00:00:00 +0000

